{"type": "article", "id": 19553, "title": "脚踏式洗衣机", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-23T07:37:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021123461PBKeD7LAbCIMpcO.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是加拿大设计团队 Yirego 推出的脚踏式洗衣机，只有一个电饭煲的大小，适合单身或宿舍群居的人使用。它有快速清洗小件物品的功能，一次可以容纳一件牛仔裤或 6 件T-恤。使用时需要打开盖子依次放进衣服、水和洗衣液，再脚踩一下踏板，就可以运作了。清洗时间大概 5 到 10 分钟，定价 239 美元起，<a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/drumi-the-foot-powered-washing-machine#/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150017xIjAMDzFa5RGVH91.gif\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150025yqhGlHz5TBwsQS2V.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150026KBCcDA0j6MwhkUv2.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}